section.def:
committee
                (委員會) means a committee of the Council
            established under section 9;

content.def:
OLIO (《香港公開進修學院條例》) means The Open Learning Institute of Hong Kong
                        Ordinance
                        (Cap. 1145) that was in force immediately before 30 May 1997;

subparagraph.content:
an affirmative vote of a majority of those members present and not
                    disqualified from voting on the matter shall be required for the passing of a
                    resolution;
